      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It's in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for something truly special and spotless, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel! \u2728",
      "price": 45500.0,
