    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS timing. This specimen boasts a documented subframe reinforcement and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivering power through a factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains perfectly taut with original bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the high-revving powerplant maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history, this E46 represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement in flawless mechanical and cosmetic form.",
